# Contact form delivery via Web3Forms (https://web3forms.com) — free, no account.
#
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com and enter YOUR email address.
# 2. You'll instantly receive an "Access Key" by email.
# 3. Paste it below, then copy this file to `.env` (or set it in Vercel).
#
# The key is public by design (it only lets the form send to your verified
# inbox), so it is safe to commit / expose in the client bundle.
# If left unset, the contact form gracefully falls back to a mailto: link.

VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
